column4: Feels good to get back on the right track. Sometimes u gotta make sumthin outta nothing...
Thank u to everybody that showed me love the past few months.. Been tough but I'm ready for the new challenge ahead of me.. Let's go!
“@amycox1: @kyleweaver5 Congrats!!  You just keep movin closer to Pullman!  Maybe it's a sign!” maybe??
Struggle builds strength.. Gotta stay strong..
Gotta love the grind... Learning more about me everyday..
